Copilot_Goldilocks_UIZoom_750px.gif" src="/getattachment/cbeaff52-90fb-43c5-bd4c-31286be4a725/Copilot_Goldilocks_UIZoom_750px.gif" style="width: 750px; height: 492px;" title="Copilot_Goldilocks_UIZoom_750px.gif" /></p><p paraeid="{ec5c69ae-2950-4cb0-8f64-5e00fb6041b4}{141}" paraid="354526591">自 12 月以来，我们稳步迈向实现这一愿景，并将商业数据保护资格扩大到更多教师用户以及 18 岁及以上的学生，帮助释放高等教育机构生成式 AI 的力量。</p><p paraeid="{ec5c69ae-2950-4cb0-8f64-5e00fb6041b4}{197}" paraid="1513651461">今天，我们很高兴与大家分享我们的下一波可用性。从 2 月下旬开始，拥有以下 Microsoft 许可证的用户在使用其工作或学校 (Entra ID) 帐户登录时，将有资格在 Copilot 中获得商业数据保护，无需支付额外费用： </p><ul role="list"><li aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="0" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="1" role="listitem"><p paraeid="{ec5c69ae-2950-4cb0-8f64-5e00fb6041b4}{227}" paraid="301228303">微软 365 F1 </p></li><li aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="0" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;335559991&quot;:360,&quot;469769226&quot;:&quot;Symbol&quot;,&quot;469769242&quot;:[8226],&quot;469777803&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;469777804&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;469777815&quot;:&quot;hybridMultilevel&quot;}" data-listid="1" role="listitem"><p paraeid="{ec5c69ae-2950-4cb0-8f64-5e00fb6041b4}{234}" paraid="24837646">微软 Office 365 E1/E1 Plus/E3/E5/F3 </p></li><li aria-setsize="-1" data-aria-level="1" data-aria-posinset="0" data-font="Symbol" data-leveltext="" data-list-defn-props="{&quot;335551671&quot;:0,&quot;335552541&quot;:1,&quot;335559684&quot;:-2,&quot;335559685&quot;:720,&quot;33555999